Class ILPModelCPLEX

  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    PetriNetILPModel, PetriNetSingleILPModel

    public abstract class ILPModelCPLEX
extends ilog.opl.IloCustomOplDataSource
    This abstract class provides a model for the ILP problem. It can be overwritten for a specific ILP problem model.
    Author:
    T. van der Wiel
